generic_name: ANTICOAGULANT CITRATE PHOSPHATE DEXTROSE SOLUTION WITH AS-1
warnings: WARNING Avoid contact with sharp objects. DO NOT USE if the overwrap or blood bag system shows any signs of deterioration. DO NOT USE if the solutions are not clear. Dispose of all system components that have been contaminated with blood in a biohazard container as per your institution's SOP. Dispose of all sharps as per your institution's SOP.
